Time for our next notes, F, E and D

Take some time now to play F E and D on
your own and practice holding these
notes for as long as you can with a pure
tone.

As you go lower on the flute, you're going
to have to change your mouth a little.  Try
frowning slightly and opening your mouth
slightly to make the lower notes sound
more pure.

Let's practice these low notes with some
exercises.
